@Nofish: Please see my first pull request:
https://github.com/HelloZeroNet/ZeroMe/pull/66

@Mkg20001: I suggest you to attach user link in mentions. And to we not need to use ":" after the username.

@Yinyue: I agree with implement some features from ZeroMe+.
Rename the "Following" tab to "Relevant", add the "Random" and "Search", support Hashtags, can flag posts as "Bad Ugly" and "Spam", change "Mute" to "Block" button near the "Follow", "Likes" tab after "Posts" tab in profile, and the general options menu.
Oh, who created ZeroMe+?
@Mkg20001: I think you can find the ZeroMe+ repository and push the changes to your repo.
